  "remarks": "KPi.013. Former Director of the Second Academy of Natural Sciences (SANS). Former head of the DPRK’s long-range missile program. Choe Chun-sik was the director of the Second Academy of Natural Sciences (SANS) and was the head of the DPRK’s long-range missile program.; Listing: First listed on 02/03/2016 (amended on 26/07/2022, 16/08/2023)",
